description:
Amazing Discoveries™ is a registered non-profit organization in Canada and the US (501c3) committed to exposing deceptions and errors in the religious realm, history, science, media, and health. 

Amazing Discoveries is also broadcasting on satellite (Galaxy G-19), the name of the channel is ADtv.

Visit our website at http://amazingdiscoveries.org/
